{"type": "article", "id": 29388, "title": "藤原浩将新开概念店，以及，一个户外和旅行结合的品牌不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-11T04:14:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 1618, "name": "赞助"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 3313, "name": "洛杉矶"}, {"id": 3593, "name": "户外"}, {"id": 7721, "name": "滑板"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 19764, "name": "街头品牌"}, {"id": 30008, "name": "工业设计师"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 3862, "name": "法拉利"}, {"id": 6787, "name": "Victoria’s Secret"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 10699, "name": "L Brands"}, {"id": 17669, "name": "HUF"}, {"id": 18475, "name": "Isabel Marant"}, {"id": 21401, "name": "雷朋"}, {"id": 18765, "name": "藤原浩"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160711104009POVFgEXT19LwNJU5.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/the-parking-ginza-midnight-market-concept-store\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>藤原浩将新开概念店</b></a>｜去年 the POOL aoyama 店铺结业后，2016 年 3 月藤原浩随即在银座 SONY 大楼地下停车场开出了更大型的潮流杂货店铺 THE PARK・ING GINZA。近日藤原浩宣布将于 7 月 15 日午夜新开一家 THE PARK・ING GINZA，名为 “Midnight Market”。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/clothing-furnishings/esq-clothing-bespoke-custom-e-commerce-ge-wang10483241-10483241/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Esq Clothing 推出电商网站</b></a>｜芝加哥的 Esq Clothing 由华裔设计师 Ge Wang 创立，为一些 NBA、NFA 球星及专业运动员提供定制西装服务，近日推出了首个电商网站。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1467898943799.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>维秘 6 月获 6% 同店增长</b></a>｜Victoria’s Secret 在截至 7 月 2 日的前五周内，获得 6% 的同店销售增长，PINK 由于促销销售强劲，抵消泳衣和服装类的疲软。母公司 L Brands 整体同店销售也录得 6% 的增幅，超出预期的 2.1%。净销售额上涨了 7.4% 达到 12.96 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Ray-Ban-signs-sponsorship-agreement-with-Ferrari,712020.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雷朋与法拉利签署赞助协议｜</b></a>Ferrari N.V.  宣布与 Luxottica 集团签署赞助协议，雷朋太阳镜（Ray-Ban）将成为 SF16-H 一级方程式赛车赞助商。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/balenciaga-beverly-hills-store-rodeo-drive-10484325/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga 在洛杉矶开新旗舰店</a>，位于比佛利山庄，此前洛杉矶的旗舰店于 2008 年开业，当时的创意总监还是 Nicolas&nbsp;Ghesquière。</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711103352X3YDycTNIokP2Q8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.786133\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711103356DMcW172FxU6Bn8EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.272461\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711103358IEZsro8yWeRBahOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.852539\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607111033044REZWw2hfSlrToe7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.786133\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">Michael Kors 找来了超模 Freja Beha Erichsen 拍摄<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/michael-kors-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">品牌秋冬系列广告</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607111024514H6e2rYNPjaqcg1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711102452OU89Amj4D5Ty6Yaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711102454N8tMvfOD1cCBUdPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/opening-ceremony-vans-shop-in-shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 近日在 Opening Ceremony 的纽约旗舰店内开设“店中店”</a>，由工业设计师&nbsp;Max Lamb 设计:<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711092539EZ36G5IcLa2vq8Dp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711092542mIVeFvs9AUnHrZwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711092543ZhmclHNKqd9xn1RA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071109254449XcKdDUt2QHwgSu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/gallery/isabel-marant-resort-10484019/#!23/isabel-marant-resort-2017-23/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Isabel Marant 2017 早春度假系列</a>：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711103545w54SyRAc1HxLDZ3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711103546HaSRtYc4xoqFTPMu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711103547YPb4HVNfLUdSFoW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p>日本户外品牌 Ficouture 2009 年创立，最近将品牌的旅行、户外和家居产品线整合，更名为 F/CE，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/ficouture-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">发布了秋冬系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083031Sylx1gTAOYPrb6Qv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083033QirAIB4d6pL5oNEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083034F4w5ZdmJyKcWRN0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083043rW6pQeA5vBFioY31.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083053La5d24wpjtSMlXQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083135QwuR7d3DiZn9gmKM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711083136wPEZvJTRSkgr54qQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">美国街头品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/huf-2016-fall-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">HUF 发布今年秋冬系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084829ZDtQxMwBJu4nj2PL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084829dsCVYfRp7H8nxiUk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084830XaC8MsrS5lynGmBJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084832kxqn4HSjsC5J0EWR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084833hAwUK68OTfNapysE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084833VKOxedU10qiLmSrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711084833M1X6wSYClbWQtDZB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\